13 0 obj
<< /Length 917 >>
stream
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 128.64 590 Td (UNDERSTANDING CHRONIC PAIN) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 50 580 m 382 580 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 555 Td (Chronic pain is REAL. It is not 'in your head.') Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 50 537 Td (Gate Control Theory \(simplified\):) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 9 Tf 50 515 Td (Your brain has a 'gate' that controls how much pain signal gets through.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 9 Tf 50 501 Td (Things that OPEN the gate \(more pain\): stress, poor sleep, fear, focus) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 9 Tf 50 487 Td (Things that CLOSE the gate \(less pain\): relaxation, distraction, movement) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 50 465 Td (PAIN vs SUFFERING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 9 Tf 50 449 Td (Pain = the physical sensation \(you may not control this fully\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 9 Tf 50 435 Td (Suffering = the mental/emotional response \(you CAN influence this\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 421 Td (This journal helps you manage BOTH.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
